206	## Pipeline Architecture
207	
208	```
209	football-data.org v4                Raw CSVs                    Training Data
210	       │                               │                              │
211	       ▼                               ▼                              ▼
212	 FootballClient ──► Builders ──► dataset/csv/*.csv ──► DataCleaner ──► train_data.csv
213	 (circuit-breaker,              │                                       │
214	  rate-limited,                 │                    ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────┐
215	  X-Auth-Token)                 │                    ▼                  ▼                   ▼
216	                                │              ClassifierFactory  DistributionFitter
217	                                │                    │                  │
218	                                │                    ▼                  ▼
219	                                │              *.joblib           distributions.json
220	                                │                    │                  │
221	                                │                    ▼                  ▼
222	                                │              GamePredictor ◄──── FeatureSampler
223	                                │                    │
224	                                │                    ▼
225	                                │           TournamentSimulator
226	                                │              (Monte Carlo,
227	                                │               single-match ties)
228	                                │                    │
229	                                │                    ▼
230	                                │              RoundResult
231	                                │                    │
232	                                │                    ▼
233	                                │              ResultPlotter
234	                                │                    │
235	                                │                    ▼
236	                                │           bracket.png + probabilities.png
237	```
238	
239	The `Pipeline` orchestrator wires all stages together. Each stage is independently runnable via the CLI, and intermediate artifacts (CSVs, `.joblib` models, `distributions.json`) are persisted to disk so stages can be re-run in isolation.
240	
