4	
5	- Dataset names: teams, matches, ranking, players, match_details
6	  (replaces: teams, games, ranking, players, games_details)
7	- Round names: Round of 32 / Round of 16 / Quarter-finals / Semi-finals / Final
8	- ``SimulationConfig`` carries only ``{n_simulations, classifier}`` — no series fields.
9	- ``build_players_csv`` uses ``competition`` kwarg, not ``season``.
10	- Commands renamed: build-games -> build-matches, build-games-details -> build-match-details.
11	"""
12	
